name: Mutualize
description: A Holochain app for Asset backed mutual credit

attestation.properties: attestation entry to vouch for the last transaction of an agent

offer.properties: offer private entry to temporarily store the data of a transaction before accepting it

transaction.properties: private transactions that are the base to compute the total balance

USERNAME.properties: this is the username of the agent

holochain_anchors::anchor.properties: Anchors are used as the base for links so linked entries can be found with a text search.
